gov.nih.nci.cabig.caaers.web.fields
Interface InputField

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractInputField, BasePropertyInputFieldGroup.InputFieldWrapper, CompositeField, InputFieldFactory.DefaultInputField, QualifiedPropertyNameInputField, RepeatingFieldGroupFactory.RepeatingFieldGroup.InputFieldWrapper
public interface InputField

Collects the basic information about a form field in a Spring MVC application. The goal is for fields to be (mostly) rendered automatically and consistently, including labels and the "required" indicator.

Also enables (but does not implement) some simple automatic validation (via the required flag).

Author:
Rhett Sutphin, Biju Joseph
See Also:
TabWithFields, InputFieldGroup
